05-15T12:17:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>一間都未去過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n一樣....</blockquote><br />\nX3<br />\n利申住左廿幾年"},{"pid":"0788677049eb446ae462e39c5c7ccea2485b8f4b","tid":244313,"uid":93269,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-15T14:52:58.000Z","msg":"沙田18 服務好，質素高，食片皮鴨一流。<br />\n<br />\n沙田大會堂間bar, 都係美心旗下， Lunch Set 大概100蚊樓下，味道普通，但勝在夠清靜唔洗迫，同朋友食飯影相就啱。夜晚好浪漫，會同另一半去食。<br />\n<br />\n科學園間bar 價錢唔貴，不過上次去中午先開，味道中上，拍拖去幾舒服。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1cb6adc4dfd0e3558aaad4689ec43c9f8ffbda94","tid":244313,"uid":1858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-15T16:14:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>一間都未去過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n一樣....</blockquote><br />\n剩係知義大利菜係圖書館附近個間</blockquote><br />\n美心皇宮右邊條梯上<br />\n食過幾次覺得okay，坐出面望到成個城門河景，好靚，但係d人好似多數坐入面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申  非打手"}]}